{"tid":1846043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣禁香港人入境？！","createTime":"2020-01-27T12:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T13:23:01.000Z","uid":167567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f68a23efc745ac35fc03813771eeb257ca743f","tid":1846043,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppqxcer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fppqxcer.png&h=41e7e05f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禁支那人又好<br />\n真係禁港人都好<br />\n台灣既做法係完全正確！咁先可以保障到自己國民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果台灣依家只係禁支那人入台<br />\n而香港唔封關既話<br />\n好快就會禁香港人入台！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家我哋要做既就係三罷迫政府封關<br />\n仲唔三罷！<br />\n遲下全球都禁香港入境！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全港三罷救港呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxLxcgU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxLxcgU.jpg&h=d5543056&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbsLxgV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbsLxgV.jpg&h=59ea7551&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqFQJoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtqFQJoB.jpg&h=c68b21ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqiCooB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqiCooB.jpg&h=c666e386&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yHWkmah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyHWkmah.jpg&h=a110b9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrJuYWY.jpg\" d